page.title: 18Families.
page.content: In my family there are:- me, my Mum,my Dad and my dog Sally. On my Mum's side there are my nanny, my grandad, 2 brothers and 5 sisters. One of Mum's brothers died when he was little. He would have been the youngest but my Mum is now. On my Dad's side there is him and his one sister and my Grandad. My nana died last Christmas. My Mum and Dad own a dance studio,{The {Lollipop Dance Studio, }but I do see them often. My Dad's family live in Skegness and Boston. My Mum's family all live in Yorkshire. I was born in Sydney, Australia. My Dad was born in Boston and my Mum was born in Brighouse. There are 15 years between the ages of my Mum and Dad. I am 11. By Emma Victoria Horry.
